tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name TEXT,
    customer_name TEXT,
    order_date TIMESTAMP,
    status VARCHAR(10) 
);
orders(id INT PRIMARY KEY, order_number VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL, customer_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL, status VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL)
order_items(id INT PRIMARY KEY, order_id INT NOT NULL, product_id INT NOT NULL, quantity INT NOT NULL, price DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL)
products(id INT PRIMARY KEY, product_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL, description TEXT, price DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL)
customers(id INT PRIMARY KEY, customer_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL, email VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL, phone_number VARCHAR(20))
statuses(id INT PRIMARY KEY, status_code VARCHAR(25) NOT NULL, description TEXT)
